        {
            "title": "A股近全日高位收市  深股一周升3.56%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股收升，滬股全日高位收市，深股曾見13000，兩市合計15857.96億元(人民幣‧下同)。一周累計滬股升近1.5%，深股升逾3.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-12.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-12.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指收升13點或0.34%，報3888點，為全日高位，今早開報3870，跌5點或0.13%，早段見3856點，跌19點或0.49%，為全日低位，隨即向上轉升，午後升破上午高位，全日成交6457.56億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指全日報12984點，升108點或0.85%，今早開報12869，跌6點或0.05%，早段見12834，跌41點或0.32%，即節節向上，午後高見13000，升125點或0.97%，全日成交9400.4億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300收報11點或0.25%，報4526點 ; 創業板指數升21點或0.7%，報3052點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">一周累計滬股升54點或1.41% ; 深股一周升446點或3.56%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15464698-a%e8%82%a1%e8%bf%91%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e9%ab%98%e4%bd%8d%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e5%8d%873-56",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-14.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-28 15:45:32",
